text: Jūlija Tepliha or Julia Teplih (born June 26, 1984 in Riga, Latvia) is a Latvian figure skater. She is the 2001 Latvian national champion. ==External links== * Category:Latvian female single skaters Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Riga
title: Jūlija Tepliha
